    "body": "Fixes what I believe #7721 was hinting at before an LLM (re?)wrote it to have a reproducer that doesn't reproduce and a bunch of incorrect speculation about the cause.\r\n\r\nThe saved class cell was applied with the result of the decorator rather than the result of the class before the decorator.",
